snippet.title: "Starbear: Taxi" (MobileVR) - Launch Video
snippet.description:
"Starbear: Taxi" is A fast-paced, VR-native title that really delivers. Race a spaceship taxi around Starbear’s tiny, futuristic city to deliver busy bear passengers to their desired destinations. Bears gotta be places too, you know?!

Available NOW on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/702030/Starbear_Taxi/

Available NOW on Oculus Rift:
https://www.oculus.com/experiences/rift/1458496604197649/

Also available on Oculus Go, GearVR, and Google Daydream. PSVR version coming soon!
